the subtracted term under the square root is nonnegative, we get
\begin{equation}
E_0
\le
\frac{
\kappa L\sqrt{\lambda^4+6\lambda^3+7\lambda^2+\lambda}
}{
1-eL\left|\tan\!\left(\frac{\kappa f(\lambda)}{2}\right)\right|
}.
\end{equation}
