\ket{\psi_{\mathrm{true}}^{(L)}}-\ket{\psi_{\mathrm{online}}^{(L)}}
\right\|_2
\le
\mathcal{O}(\delta)+\varepsilon,
\end{equation}
which proves \eqref{eq:simple-small-kappa-error}.

